data.description: ***SELLER OFFERING $10K IN RATE BUY DOWN OPTIONS***  Come take a look at this spacious and inviting basement ranch home in the county on almost 7/10ths of an acre.  Featuring a main level with a split bedroom plan, huge master suite with en suite bath, jetted tub & separate shower, large walk in closet.  The vaulted great room is open to the dining and kitchen area features all new stainless steel appliances.  The finished basement features a large multipurpose space great for a recreation room or additional living quarters.  Currently being used as a personal gym and office the finished room is over 1000sf.  with a separate full bath and a bedroom or office with a large walk in closet.  Outside you will find a new deck, as well as an above ground pool and decking (new in 2023) plus a detached storage shed or workshop.  All situated on a large lot backing up to a wooded mountain view.  The neighborhood also features a common area with a fishing pond.  Call for your private tour today!
